tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Influencers (
    influencer_id INT,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(255),
    partnership_id INT,
    social_media_platform VARCHAR(255),
    followers_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE ad_engagement (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_id INT,
    influencer_id INT,
    engagement_type TEXT,
    engagement_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE Advertisers (
    advertiser_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    advertiser_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Influencers (
    influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    social_media_handle VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Ads (
    ad_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    ad_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    ad_cost DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Engagements (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_id INT,
    influencer_id INT,
    engagement_date DATE,
    engagement_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE AdPerformance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ad_id INT,
    engagement_id INT,
    clicks INT DEFAULT 0,
    conversions INT DEFAULT 0
)
